text: The Javanese Wikipedia (Javanese Wikipedia basa Jawa) is the Javanese-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition started in March 2004. As of July 2013, it has over 44,000 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Javanese Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2004
